{
  "stem": "10272.7",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we understood each other very nice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she was a nice lady.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I moved into her apartment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we lived together for a while.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after a year, there's a boy-- she got pregnant.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a boy was born.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we named him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she was not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "His name was Jirka, which-- they made it out of-- from my Hebrew name, Yitzhak, they figure that the name is George of English.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And George is-- in Czech is Jirka.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they named him Jirka.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And since we were not married, he took the name of, of his mother, the family name, Jirka Kuchar, K-U-C-H-A-R.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I lived-- it was in '48 he was born.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in-- and in '49, he was already a year old.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I took care of him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I, I raised him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I helped Marie to take care of him and everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So in '49-- in '48, broke out the war in Israel, in Palestine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Israel was declared an independent state.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And Arabs attacked the country.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And Israel was in a very-- state of emergency because America wouldn't supply arms for, for the Jewish state to defend themselves.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Nobody, no state in the world would supply arms.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Only the, the Czechoslovakians.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was-- the Secretary of the Communist party was a Jew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he secretly--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name was Slansky, Rudolf Slansky.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His Jewish name was Saltzman.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was from my-- from my-- from the Carpathian-- from this area where I am from, from Muncazs or from Ungra, somewhere.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he turned out to be in Moscow during the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a very able man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he-- and they, they-- the Russians put him as the Secretary of the Communist Party of Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was very popular.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But came the war came with-- in Israel, he was the guy who supplied arms secretly, probably with the approval of, of the Russians, too.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He supplied these arms to Israel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Secretly, because we went illegally to-- we went there without approval of, of the Russians.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, so I go there-- I got there, to Israel, with this Haganah.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I got there in Israel, the, the war didn't stop, but was a cease-fire.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I wrote back to this Marie that she, she want to join me, she can come.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But she said, no, there is a war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I found another boy who wants to marry me with this-- with this kid-- with the child.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she didn't come.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She didn't join me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in the meantime, I, I served in the Israeli Army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I-- when I was-- I left the Army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I joined the Israeli police force.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the police force, I met Betty.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She came as a, a new immigrant from Romania in this town where I served as a policeman.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There we met.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we married.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We married.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had two kids-- two girls, one boy who, who died after one day in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He died.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He passed away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So these two girls and my wife, we moved to another town near Tel Aviv.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we-- in Tel Aviv, we-- I worked.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I left the Israeli Army-- the Israeli police.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I worked as a bookkeeper in the huge-- in the biggest supply, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] supply company called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there, in [NON-ENGLISH], I was also-- took part-- while I was working in the police, I served also in another war in 1956.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They call it the Sinai War.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It lasted also a few weeks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then in 1967, I served in the Six Day War as an officer of communication.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I was trained to be a [NON-ENGLISH]-- communication officer in the police, working on the-- on the-- on the-- on the radio as a radio operator-- signals and decoding and keeping up the communications between all the-- all the-- all the other police stations and patrolling the, the streets of Jerusalem and Tel Aviv.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was-- at that time, I was serving in the Six Day War-- the Six Day War.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "After the Six Day War was over-- and serving as an officer-- it came 1979, when my cousin from Los Angeles came to visit Israel.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said to me, come and-- you are having a hard time here to making ends meet.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I will send you a ticket.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Come and take a look at America.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You're American.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Your father was American citizen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why not come and see America?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I came as a visitor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I got from my job in, in [NON-ENGLISH], I got-- I got permission to visit America and then-- for six months without pay.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I could leave.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I would leave my job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I promised to come back in six months.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
